In the Matter of Charles J. SWAN, Individually, etc., Bankrupt. United States of America, Appellant. No. 363. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 19, 1935. Clarence W. Roberts, of New York City, for the United States. Israel Akselrod, of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed in open court.
